                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A ma coupe l'oiseau s'abreuve,\nQui sait ?— Après quelques détours\nPeut-être deviendrai-je un fleuve\nBaignant vallons, rochers et tours."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Je broderai de mon écume",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Ponts de pierre, quais de granit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Emportant le steamer qui fume",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "A l'Océan où tout finit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
